{"messages": [{"role": "system", "content": "You are an NSP (Network Services Platform) intent configuration assistant. Given a natural language description of a network service, output a JSON object with three fields: 'intent_type' (one of: epipe, tunnel, vprn), 'template_name' (the NSP template to use), and 'fill_values' (a flat dictionary of field paths and their values that should be filled into the intent template). Only include fields that differ from template defaults. Use dot notation for nested paths and [N] for array indices. Output only valid JSON, no explanations."}, {"role": "user", "content": "I need a Layer 3 VPN for customer 1532. Name it 'VPRN-4425-DeepRoute'. There's one site on device 192.168.174.237 with service ID 4425. Use RD 64754:4425, import policy DeepRoute-VRF-Import and export policy DeepRoute-VRF-Export. The interfaces are: Theta-Cluster-Master on port 2/1/c11/1 with IP 10.128.123.12/31; Theta-Cluster-Worker-1 on port 1/2/c1/4 with IP 10.210.169.26/30; Theta-Cluster-Worker-2 on port lag-AMD10-4x10GE with IP 100.121.84.7/30."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\n  \"intent_type\": \"vprn\",\n  \"template_name\": \"VPRNServiceTemplate\",\n  \"fill_values\": {\n    \"service-name\": \"VPRN-4425-DeepRoute\",\n    \"customer-id\": 1532,\n    \"site[0].site-name\": \"VPRN-4425-DeepRoute\",\n    \"site[0].device-id\": \"192.168.174.237\",\n    \"site[0].ne-service-id\": 4425,\n    \"site[0].route-distinguisher\": \"64754:4425\",\n    \"site[0].vrf-import\": [\n      \"DeepRoute-VRF-Import\"\n    ],\n    \"site[0].vrf-export\": [\n      \"DeepRoute-VRF-Export\"\n    ],\n    \"site[0].interface[0].interface-name\": \"Theta-Cluster-Master\",\n    \"site[0].interface[0].sap.port-id\": \"2/1/c11/1\",\n    \"site[0].interface[0].ipv4.primary.address\": \"10.128.123.12\",\n    \"site[0].interface[0].ipv4.primary.prefix-length\": 31,\n    \"site[0].interface[1].interface-name\": \"Theta-Cluster-Worker-1\",\n    \"site[0].interface[1].sap.port-id\": \"1/2/c1/4\",\n    \"site[0].interface[1].ipv4.primary.address\": \"10.210.169.26\",\n    \"site[0].interface[1].ipv4.primary.prefix-length\": 30,\n    \"site[0].interface[2].interface-name\": \"Theta-Cluster-Worker-2\",\n    \"site[0].interface[2].sap.port-id\": \"lag-AMD10-4x10GE\",\n    \"site[0].interface[2].ipv4.primary.address\": \"100.121.84.7\",\n    \"site[0].interface[2].ipv4.primary.prefix-length\": 30\n  }\n}"}]}
