{"messages": [{"role": "system", "content": "You are an NSP (Network Services Platform) intent configuration assistant. Given a natural language description of a network service, output a JSON object with three fields: 'intent_type' (one of: epipe, tunnel, vprn), 'template_name' (the NSP template to use), and 'fill_values' (a flat dictionary of field paths and their values that should be filled into the intent template). Only include fields that differ from template defaults. Use dot notation for nested paths and [N] for array indices. Output only valid JSON, no explanations."}, {"role": "user", "content": "We need a new L3 VPN service for customer 2315. The service is called 'VPRN-9432-UltraPath' with one site at 192.168.242.52. NE service ID: 9432. RD: 65336:9432. VRF import: UltraPath-VRF-Import, export: UltraPath-VRF-Export. Please configure these interfaces: Apollo-Cluster-Master on port lag-Dell-NAR1-4x25GE with IP 172.18.109.231/30; Apollo-Cluster-Worker-1 on port lag-Intel7-2x25GE with IP 10.78.180.199/28; Apollo-Cluster-Worker-2 on port lag-Nokia8-4x25GE with IP 10.239.151.55/28."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\n  \"intent_type\": \"vprn\",\n  \"template_name\": \"VPRNServiceTemplate\",\n  \"fill_values\": {\n    \"service-name\": \"VPRN-9432-UltraPath\",\n    \"customer-id\": 2315,\n    \"site[0].site-name\": \"VPRN-9432-UltraPath\",\n    \"site[0].device-id\": \"192.168.242.52\",\n    \"site[0].ne-service-id\": 9432,\n    \"site[0].route-distinguisher\": \"65336:9432\",\n    \"site[0].vrf-import\": [\n      \"UltraPath-VRF-Import\"\n    ],\n    \"site[0].vrf-export\": [\n      \"UltraPath-VRF-Export\"\n    ],\n    \"site[0].interface[0].interface-name\": \"Apollo-Cluster-Master\",\n    \"site[0].interface[0].sap.port-id\": \"lag-Dell-NAR1-4x25GE\",\n    \"site[0].interface[0].ipv4.primary.address\": \"172.18.109.231\",\n    \"site[0].interface[0].ipv4.primary.prefix-length\": 30,\n    \"site[0].interface[1].interface-name\": \"Apollo-Cluster-Worker